Package org.openbel.framework.common.download

Common classes for handling resource downloads.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DownloadHandler DownloadHandler defines a class responsible for downloading the contents of a url and associated checksum if provided.
 

Class Summary
DownloadFile DownloadFile defines a downloaded file with an optional SHA-256 checksum value to validate the downloaded cdata.
FileDownloadHandler FileProtocolHandler implements an AbstractProtocolHandler to download a resource from a file:// url.
HttpDownloadHandler  
 

Enum Summary
SupportedProtocol SupportedProtocol defines the url schemes supported by the OpenBEL Framework.
 

Exception Summary
DownloadError A BEL error indicating download of a resource resulted in an error.
